name: ED TORQ
description: Revealed at Geneva Motor Show as world's first self driving racing car, integrated on Asphalt 8 by Gameloft, ED TORQ pioneers eMOTORSPORT 3.0, a DAeMO (decentralized autonomous eMOTORSPORT organization) built by experts, owned by fans and fueled by web 3. QOIN is required for every entry fee, sponsorship placement (liveries, naming rights, broadcast slots), and purchase of official products or services. Staked QOIN enables voting on all protocol-level proposals (ticket pricing, revenue splits, global deals, track creation, burns).
